1
00:01:26,220 --> 00:01:29,260
" Princess Silver "

2
00:01:29,522 --> 00:01:31,824
Episode 50

3
00:01:32,740 --> 00:01:34,455
Luo Yan.

4
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:37,290
Have you been outside for too long...

5
00:01:37,674 --> 00:01:39,354
until you've forgotten
about your aspiration?

6
00:01:39,517 --> 00:01:40,963
I haven't forgotten about it.

7
00:01:41,100 --> 00:01:43,102
You once asked me...

8
00:01:43,417 --> 00:01:45,388
about my wish.

9
00:01:46,556 --> 00:01:48,619
My parents died in war.

10
00:01:48,833 --> 00:01:50,885
I wish that there will be
no more war in this world.

11
00:01:51,023 --> 00:01:53,848
You said that you have
the same wish as I have.

12
00:01:56,524 --> 00:01:58,873
" The Books of Mountains and Rivers "

13
00:02:00,661 --> 00:02:02,356
Now,

14
00:02:03,581 --> 00:02:05,401
I choose to accept this alliance...

15
00:02:06,839 --> 00:02:08,703
in order to fulfil that wish.

16
00:02:11,040 --> 00:02:13,428
But this is against the act
of kindness and right conduct.

17
00:02:13,715 --> 00:02:15,409
Kindness and right conduct?

18
00:02:15,532 --> 00:02:17,412
What is kindness and right conduct?

19
00:02:18,399 --> 00:02:21,304
Back then, when I had saved you,
kept you,

20
00:02:21,589 --> 00:02:24,240
let you stay in the manor and
taught you how to read and fight,

21
00:02:24,331 --> 00:02:25,545
that was kindness.

22
00:02:25,636 --> 00:02:28,025
Because of me, you had stayed
in Northern Realm for years,

23
00:02:28,157 --> 00:02:31,046
you had endured humiliation
until finally, you got the book.

24
00:02:31,205 --> 00:02:32,659
That was right conduct.

25
00:02:32,805 --> 00:02:35,852
Our original intention is to get
The Book of Mountains and Rivers...

26
00:02:36,206 --> 00:02:38,511
and take over the world honourably.

27
00:02:39,267 --> 00:02:40,769
But until now,

28
00:02:40,872 --> 00:02:42,599
we still can't unearth
the secret of the book...

29
00:02:42,690 --> 00:02:44,951
although we already
had it for one year.

30
00:02:45,323 --> 00:02:48,101
We can't continue with
this path anymore.

31
00:02:48,970 --> 00:02:51,093
We can't be stubborn about it anymore.

32
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,139
Luo Yan.

33
00:02:53,426 --> 00:02:54,907
You are different from other woman.

34
00:02:54,998 --> 00:02:56,621
So, you should know better that...

35
00:02:56,712 --> 00:02:59,243
discarding smaller righteousness
for bigger righteousness...

36
00:02:59,498 --> 00:03:02,188
is the best way for a person who
is meant to do great things.

37
00:03:03,938 --> 00:03:05,243
Now,

38
00:03:05,361 --> 00:03:08,155
someone has presented
this shortcut to us.

39
00:03:08,474 --> 00:03:10,240
We can achieve
our aspiration with it...

40
00:03:10,331 --> 00:03:12,918
while reducing the number of soldiers
that we have to sacrifice.

41
00:03:14,764 --> 00:03:16,141
Why not do it?

42
00:03:16,232 --> 00:03:18,285
But if we can't be righteous
in the smaller scale,

43
00:03:18,383 --> 00:03:20,221
we can forget about
bigger righteousness.

44
00:03:20,714 --> 00:03:24,190
You can have no qualm about
Prince Li and Rong Le's safety...

45
00:03:24,396 --> 00:03:26,251
but you have to think about
your consort's feelings.

46
00:03:26,342 --> 00:03:28,062
As long as you don't tell her,

47
00:03:28,648 --> 00:03:30,495
she won't know about it.

48
00:03:30,964 --> 00:03:32,618
But if you tell her,

49
00:03:33,024 --> 00:03:35,324
then our friendship
for so many years...

50
00:03:37,133 --> 00:03:39,053
will have to come to an end.

51
00:03:49,930 --> 00:03:51,327
Your Highness.

52
00:03:51,418 --> 00:03:53,454
I have been hiding something from you.

53
00:03:53,988 --> 00:03:55,673
Rong Le is the descendant
of Qin family.

54
00:03:55,764 --> 00:03:58,243
And she is the only one who knows
about the secret of the book.

55
00:03:58,350 --> 00:04:00,325
So, you can't kill her.

56
00:04:09,315 --> 00:04:10,575
That day, in the inn,

57
00:04:10,666 --> 00:04:12,451
you were the one who
arranged for someone...

58
00:04:12,542 --> 00:04:14,419
to disguise as me to
lure away the soldiers?

59
00:04:15,007 --> 00:04:16,633
If I can issue an arrest warrant,

60
00:04:16,724 --> 00:04:19,564
I can make sure that you
won't be caught for sure.

61
00:04:22,924 --> 00:04:26,336
I wonder who are the people that
had disguised as the Seven Asuras.

62
00:04:26,552 --> 00:04:28,559
They look exactly
the same on the surface.

63
00:04:28,943 --> 00:04:30,838
But their martial art skills
are way off.

64
00:04:31,110 --> 00:04:32,846
I had asked The Hidden Ones
to investigate about it.

65
00:04:32,937 --> 00:04:34,634
If I'm not wrong,

66
00:04:34,872 --> 00:04:36,761
they are from the Creed of Vengeance.

67
00:04:37,314 --> 00:04:40,493
By the way, in the letter that you
had asked Xiao Sha to give me,

68
00:04:40,584 --> 00:04:42,871
you said that something is
not right with Ling Yue.

69
00:04:43,483 --> 00:04:45,783
From the moment she approaches Ya Li,

70
00:04:46,223 --> 00:04:48,137
I already feel that
something is not right.

71
00:04:48,341 --> 00:04:50,240
I'm not sure about it yet.

72
00:04:50,581 --> 00:04:52,433
But when we were in
the great hall back then,

73
00:04:52,546 --> 00:04:54,589
it looked like she was defending me.

74
00:04:54,811 --> 00:04:56,465
But actually,
she was twisting the truth.

75
00:04:56,556 --> 00:04:58,365
Her words were not persuasive at all.

76
00:04:58,688 --> 00:05:00,350
And she had planned...

77
00:05:00,441 --> 00:05:02,285
Ya Li's death as well.

78
00:05:02,367 --> 00:05:05,637
She had made sure that it'll be
impossible for me to justify myself.

79
00:05:06,150 --> 00:05:08,257
Now, we are here in Chen together.

80
00:05:08,587 --> 00:05:10,076
I want to see...

81
00:05:10,174 --> 00:05:12,274
what other evil plans
the instigator behind her...

82
00:05:12,365 --> 00:05:14,243
has for me.

83
00:05:14,413 --> 00:05:15,868
I found out that...

84
00:05:16,006 --> 00:05:19,191
that beau was sent into
the manor by Ling Yue.

85
00:05:19,690 --> 00:05:21,690
A day before, he had murdered Chun Ni.

86
00:05:21,783 --> 00:05:24,666
And then, he disguised as
Chun Ni to go into your room.

87
00:05:25,100 --> 00:05:26,785
I'm right after all.

88
00:05:27,547 --> 00:05:29,476
I treated her like my sister.

89
00:05:30,123 --> 00:05:32,031
How could she snuff out a life...

90
00:05:32,346 --> 00:05:33,992
in order to frame me?

91
00:05:34,482 --> 00:05:37,179
She was sent here as your
maidservant for the marriage alliance.

92
00:05:37,855 --> 00:05:39,117
I'm afraid that...

93
00:05:39,208 --> 00:05:42,715
since the very beginning, she has
stayed with you with ulterior motives.

94
00:05:43,146 --> 00:05:44,481
You have been together for two years.

95
00:05:44,572 --> 00:05:47,222
But she can still do
such a cruel thing to you.

96
00:05:47,343 --> 00:05:50,335
Looks like she doesn't
treat you like a sister.

97
00:05:51,222 --> 00:05:52,581
Man Yao.

98
00:05:52,860 --> 00:05:55,883
Once you have something to hold
against her, don't be soft-hearted.

99
00:06:00,433 --> 00:06:02,110
The medicine is done?

100
00:06:08,028 --> 00:06:09,527
Yes, it is.

101
00:06:09,857 --> 00:06:12,916
Look at you. You've slimmed down out
of exhaustion for the past two days.

102
00:06:13,948 --> 00:06:16,696
Give this to me.
I'll send it to the Princess.

103
00:06:17,123 --> 00:06:18,982
Go back and rest up earlier.

104
00:06:19,521 --> 00:06:20,958
You too.

105
00:06:59,198 --> 00:07:01,254
-Who is it?
-It's me, Princess.

106
00:07:01,570 --> 00:07:03,111
Come in.

107
00:07:07,366 --> 00:07:08,904
Your Highness.

108
00:07:09,514 --> 00:07:11,395
Princess, your medicine is done.

109
00:07:21,126 --> 00:07:22,673
Continue to keep
an eye on her tonight.

110
00:07:22,764 --> 00:07:25,097
