112
00:07:37,256 --> 00:07:39,169
Actually, besides Ling Yue,

113
00:07:39,349 --> 00:07:40,991
I saw the back of a person in...

114
00:07:41,082 --> 00:07:42,829
Prince Zhen Bei's manor that day.

115
00:07:43,150 --> 00:07:45,427
It looks like a person
that I know in the past.

116
00:07:45,638 --> 00:07:46,889
Chen Yu?

117
00:07:46,980 --> 00:07:48,491
You knew?

118
00:07:49,841 --> 00:07:51,391
After she took away the book,

119
00:07:51,482 --> 00:07:53,260
I had my suspicion.

120
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:57,148
Ning Qian Yi came to Zhongshan
in the name of alliance.

121
00:07:57,398 --> 00:07:59,850
And he had gone more than once
to Moon Embrace Teahouse.

122
00:07:59,988 --> 00:08:02,409
Before he came,
Chen Yu was still acting normal.

123
00:08:02,539 --> 00:08:03,980
As soon as he left,

124
