Chen Yu had kidnapped you and
forced me to give her the book.

125
00:08:07,199 --> 00:08:09,069
That was too much of a coincidence.

126
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:12,228
I had asked The Hidden Ones
to track her as well.

127
00:08:12,663 --> 00:08:14,534
And we found out that
she was last seen...

128
00:08:14,791 --> 00:08:16,687
at the border of Chen.

129
00:08:17,554 --> 00:08:19,108
