130
00:08:20,150 --> 00:08:22,127
I came here to Chen this time...

131
00:08:22,629 --> 00:08:24,809
for another thing actually.

132
00:08:25,709 --> 00:08:28,431
It is about the warhorse that
I had mentioned to you in the letter.

133
00:08:29,182 --> 00:08:30,883
Chen is famous with their warhorse.

134
00:08:31,402 --> 00:08:33,659
When Ning Qian Yi took Zhao Yun
as his wife back then,

135
00:08:33,860 --> 00:08:35,683
he had given a thousand
warhorses to Northern Realm.

136
00:08:35,774 --> 00:08:38,289
Now, these warhorses
have fallen into Fu Chou's hands.

137
00:08:38,797 --> 00:08:40,567
He wants to build
a team of elite Calvary.

138
00:08:40,982 --> 00:08:43,395
We don't have enough warhorses.
We'll be in a disadvantage.

139
00:08:43,831 --> 00:08:46,895
If we can use this chance to buy
a team of warhorses from them,

140
00:08:47,631 --> 00:08:49,845
we will be able to solve
our biggest problem.

141
00:08:52,138 --> 00:08:53,671
Wu You.

142
00:08:53,962 --> 00:08:55,867
I'm worried about Zhao Yun.

143
00:08:57,231 --> 00:08:58,974
She has fallen in love
with Ning Qian Yi...

144
00:08:59,065 --> 00:09:00,992
and she is pregnant with his child.

145
00:09:01,113 --> 00:09:02,462
If Ning Qian Yi...

146
00:09:02,568 --> 00:09:05,433
is really the one who had instructed
Chen Yu to get the book,

147
00:09:05,883 --> 00:09:08,295
tell me, what should we do then?

148
00:09:08,393 --> 00:09:09,930
Let's be sure about it first.

149
00:09:10,776 --> 00:09:12,292
Unless it's necessary,

150
00:09:12,409 --> 00:09:14,760
I won't do something that
will upset Zhao Yun.

151
00:09:16,268 --> 00:09:18,492
But if Ning Qian Yi is someone
with wild ambition,

152
00:09:18,591 --> 00:09:21,576
it won't be easy for us
to get the warhorses.

153
00:09:21,667 --> 00:09:23,118
Don't worry.

154
00:09:23,368 --> 00:09:26,264
Although Ning Qian Yi holds
the military power of Chen,

155
00:09:26,573 --> 00:09:28,558
he is not the emperor of this country.

156
00:09:29,081 --> 00:09:32,542
I already asked Leng Yan to spy
on the emperor of Chen in the palace.

157
00:09:32,898 --> 00:09:34,200
The emperor of Chen?

158
00:09:35,803 --> 00:09:38,451
He is the emperor
who has just reached...

159
00:09:38,542 --> 00:09:40,712
the age of 10 and who has
just ascended the throne?

160
00:09:41,779 --> 00:09:43,399
I heard that...

161
00:09:43,507 --> 00:09:46,872
he just knows how to have fun and
knows nothing about public affairs.

162
00:09:47,187 --> 00:09:49,837
-I wonder if it's true.
-Whether it's true or not,

163
00:09:50,007 --> 00:09:51,742
we'll know when we meet him.

164
00:09:56,300 --> 00:09:57,972
It's late already.

165
00:09:59,096 --> 00:10:00,609
I have to go.

166
00:10:02,836 --> 00:10:05,511
You have to be careful
when you stay here.

167
00:10:05,934 --> 00:10:07,669
Don't do anything risky.

168
00:10:30,235 --> 00:10:32,594
Be extra careful when you are outside.

169
