202
00:13:12,235 --> 00:13:14,928
how about we use
this chance to talk business?

203
00:13:18,992 --> 00:13:21,772
Alright, Prince Li.

204
00:13:22,547 --> 00:13:24,105
You know me?

205
00:13:24,310 --> 00:13:26,279
