spy on my actions and whereabouts?

207
00:13:34,423 --> 00:13:36,285
Not only I know about your identity,

208
00:13:36,423 --> 00:13:39,621
I know about things that happened in
Northern Realm for the past few years.

209
00:13:40,051 --> 00:13:41,897
And I know why...

210
00:13:41,988 --> 00:13:44,274
you and Prince Regent
of Northern Realm are here.

211
00:13:44,638 --> 00:13:47,535
First, it's because of
Princess Rong Le of Western Qi.

212
00:13:47,772 --> 00:13:49,759
