218
00:13:58,418 --> 00:14:01,985
I wouldn't have the chance to
experience your graceful bearing.

219
00:14:14,523 --> 00:14:17,126
How could they let a
ten-year-old take the throne?

220
00:14:17,959 --> 00:14:19,682
What are they trying to do?

221
00:14:20,135 --> 00:14:21,724
He is just a kid.

222
00:14:21,815 --> 00:14:24,651
Besides playing,
he knows hide-and-seek only.

223
00:14:27,066 --> 00:14:29,115
They let him handle
the public affairs.

224
00:14:29,558 --> 00:14:31,337
Will he be able to do it well?

225
00:14:40,573 --> 00:14:42,293
Who did His Majesty...

226
00:14:42,514 --> 00:14:44,174
encounter today?

227
00:14:46,847 --> 00:14:49,285
