in the middle of the road...

229
00:14:51,137 --> 00:14:52,836
and blocked our sight on His Majesty.

230
00:14:53,075 --> 00:14:55,968
We didn't get a clear look on
who was the person we encountered.

231
00:14:56,300 --> 00:14:57,423
But we found out that...

232
00:14:57,514 --> 00:15:00,077
the carriage belongs
to the emperor of Qi.

233
00:15:01,666 --> 00:15:03,315
Rong Qi.

234
00:15:09,474 --> 00:15:11,332
He didn't come here...

235
