to keep an eye on him?

239
00:15:22,614 --> 00:15:24,153
Send someone to check on him.

240
00:15:24,267 --> 00:15:25,589
But don't touch him.

241
00:15:25,680 --> 00:15:27,266
I don't want any other complications.

242
00:15:27,373 --> 00:15:30,174
Send someone to keep
a close eye on Fu Chou.

243
00:15:31,085 --> 00:15:32,256
By the way,

244
00:15:32,347 --> 00:15:34,818
Lin Shen told me that
Zongzheng Wu You...

245
00:15:34,909 --> 00:15:37,140
has already left southern fringe
in secret.

246
00:15:37,397 --> 00:15:40,095
Send more people to
keep an eye on him in secret.

247
00:15:40,330 --> 00:15:42,413
Report to me at once
if you find anything.

248
00:15:43,402 --> 00:15:45,211
That's it. You may leave now.

249
00:15:45,365 --> 00:15:46,648
Yes, Your Highness.

250
