" Written by Fu Yuan "

251
00:16:42,792 --> 00:16:44,227
Zhao Yun.

252
00:16:44,831 --> 00:16:46,360
What kind of a person...

253
00:16:46,451 --> 00:16:48,268
do you think Qian Yi is?

254
00:16:48,589 --> 00:16:50,168
Him?

255
00:16:50,898 --> 00:16:53,743
He is bold and righteous,
open and aboveboard,

256
